# Pets mood UI (canonical)

Read before UI work:

`docs/EMOTION_GRID_UI_ENTRY.md` · `docs/KWALIFY_FINAL_UI_BLUEPRINT.md` · `docs/KWALIFY_EMOTIONAL_SCENE_ASSEMBLY.md`

Product: `docs/KWALIFY_CREATIVE_NORTH_STAR.md` (playlist primary).

Hard rules:
- Logged-in = 2 screens: 5-card grid → fullscreen one soft illustrated object
- Spotify Pets–inspired illustration — rounded, friendly, simplified
- NOT industrial icons, NOT geometric placeholder UI, NOT world/map/compose on home
- Motion: fade + gentle scale, ease-out — no bounce
- `body.pets-app` hides legacy page chrome

Older `KWALIFY_EMOTIONAL_WORLD_UI_SPEC.md` (geometric world) is **deprecated** where it conflicts with Final UI.

